{"about_the_game":"Brew potions, doodle, and chat with the magical residents of Mangrove in <i>Apothecary</i>, a cozy puzzle game with a big heart!<br><br>As a recently hired apothecary whose recipe book has been tragically mangled, you must reverse engineer potion recipes from scratch. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552200/extras/Hair_Potion.gif?t=1694780851\" /><br><br>Test your concoctions on Roger, your friendly neighborhood test dummy!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552200/extras/RogHair.gif?t=1694780851\" /><br><br>Take notes on the walls of your workshop using Draw Mode, or doodle to your heart's content!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552200/extras/drawing_example.gif?t=1694780851\" /><br><br>Mangrove has small town drama out the wazoo, with rival gangs, forbidden love, and a contentious mayoral election. Meet a large cast of wacky characters, including tatted up fairies, potted plants, and the Mafishioso. Serve your customers correctly and you'll get paid, but consider your choices carefully. Which potions you brew for which people will determine your path forward, and which of 27 different endings you'll get.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features:</strong></h2><br>- Over 100 unique potions combinations<br>- 27 different ending variations<br>- A funky 26 song soundtrack<br>- Adorable hand drawn assets<br>- 16 weirdos to meet<br>- Free workshop kitty friend<br><br>Come visit Mangrove today!","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552200/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1694780851","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552200/page.bg.jpg?t=1694780851","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552200/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=